column4: NSLOCTEXT("[25CEAF274BD089F9C0FC6E864CFCF8DB]", "31CA7F5E408C39257BAB82838A4402F2", "I hear a voice from above. Anybody there?")
NSLOCTEXT("[25CEAF274BD089F9C0FC6E864CFCF8DB]", "1F0C259C47FCF8F80454459F540B90BE", "Help me! The ground is bulging up.")
NSLOCTEXT("[25CEAF274BD089F9C0FC6E864CFCF8DB]", "0B052C0E44CD17F5C07D00BD1D29D49E", "No, it\'s true. I hear some machinery noise.")
NSLOCTEXT("[25CEAF274BD089F9C0FC6E864CFCF8DB]", "946382AA42B7F05DFA50E5AB05CED0A3", "A machine? It must be coming from Ogremon\'s hideout.")
NSLOCTEXT("[25CEAF274BD089F9C0FC6E864CFCF8DB]", "F3EA7B8145016993F4CADCA3004155C5", "You must have done something wrong there, no?")
NSLOCTEXT("[25CEAF274BD089F9C0FC6E864CFCF8DB]", "E9F6DA634F62F50FAF529D91BCDE6AAD", "I did many things. It could be the elevator.... I\'ll go back to the hideout and check.")
